roomeq (0.3.0) bookworm; urgency=medium

  * Major API enhancements and new features
  * Migrated from FastAPI/uvicorn to Flask framework
  * Added comprehensive FFT spectral analysis functionality
  * Implemented modular FFT module (fft.py) for code organization
  * Added FFT normalization feature for relative dB measurements
  * Enhanced sine sweep generation with multiple consecutive sweeps
  * Implemented background audio recording system with secure file management
  * Added comprehensive recording management endpoints (start/stop/download/delete)
  * Fixed alsaaudio compatibility issues with PY_SSIZE_T_CLEAN macro
  * Updated comprehensive API documentation with new endpoints
  * Added windowing functions support (Hann, Hamming, Blackman)
  * Implemented frequency band analysis (sub-bass through brilliance)
  * Added peak detection and spectral centroid calculation
  * Enhanced error handling and parameter validation
  * Added CORS support for web application integration
  * Improved logging and debugging capabilities

 -- HiFiBerry <support@hifiberry.com>  Thu, 15 Aug 2025 12:00:00 +0000

